title: Lebanese MOH: Two martyrs and 15 wounded in the Zionist aggression on the suburb » Iraqi News Agency
text: Follow-up - INA The Lebanese Ministry of Health announced, today, Thursday, the martyrdom of two people and the injury of 15 others as a result of the Zionist aggression on the southern suburb of Beirut. A statement issued by the Public Health Emergency Operations Center of the Ministry of Public Health - received by the Iraqi News Agency (INA) - stated that "the Zionist enemy's raid on the southern suburb of Beirut led to the martyrdom of two people and the injury of fifteen people, including a woman in critical condition."
